Package ca.jolt.routing

Enum Class MimeInterpreter

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<MimeInterpreter>
ca.jolt.routing.MimeInterpreter
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<MimeInterpreter>, Constable
public enum MimeInterpreter extends Enum<MimeInterpreter>
Enum representing various MIME types and their associated file extensions. Provides a method to retrieve the MIME type based on a file extension.
